Package com.nandox.jop.core.processor.expression

Package contains all classes to manage jop page expression.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExpressionExecutor<E>
    Executor of an page expression.
    PageExpression
    Represent generic page expression.
    PageWriteExpression
    Represent write page expression.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPageExpression<E>
    Abstract implementation for page expression.
    BooleanPageExpression
    Boolean returned Expression Page: used for boolean page block attributes.
    CollectionPageExpression
    Page expression that return a data collection.
    ExpressionCompiler
    Compile a java expression.
    ExpressionInvoker
    Class to execute an expression.
    ExpressionValue<E>
    Expression context runtime value.
    SimplePageExpression
    Simple page expression that return a string format.

Package com.nandox.jop.core.processor.expression Description

Package contains all classes to manage jop page expression.

An page expression, like java{retrun "hello word";}.
